title: Bowling for Ballers
description: Axel and the team must intervene when Zoe's not-so-friendly bowling competition with Cleo LeBall gets interrupted by Madcap, Porcupunk, and their new cohort, the mischievously magnetic Dynamo.

title: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs/Mizzen in Action
description: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs: The girls must literally work as one to try and stop Mojo from destroying Townsville./Mizzen in Action: Captain Crack McGraigen and his crew are tossed forward in time where discover the chemical X that marks the spot and it is up to the girls and Professor to send the super-charged pirates back to their own time.

title: Some Assembly Required
description: Bugs gets a new toy with assembly required and has to learn to follow instructions.

title: The New Crystal Gems
description: Connie helps look after Beach City while Steven is busy.

title: Los Maestros Nunca se Rinden
description: Cole, la princesa Vania, Wu y los humildes llegan a un templo, que una vez fue un campo de entrenamiento para los Maestros Elementales de la Tierra.

title: Know It All
description: When Vic accidently unleashes evil bats from a cave, it's up to the boys and Don to protect the town, but Vic's know-it-all attitude keeps getting in the way.

title: #LosConejosMágicos
description: Cuando Zee le pide a Kara que cuide a sus dos conejitos mágicos, pronto comienzan a multiplicarse y a desatar el caos por toda Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Champion
description: Stuck with a problematic pet, Apple and Onion need to somehow find a way to get their lives back.

title: Te Quiero Mao Mao
description: Un solitario explosivo y su mejor amigo holgazán se desvían del viaje que los llevará a convertirse en leyenda y descubren que su historia apenas comienza.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: The Real Number One
description: When Thomas' #1 is covered by paint, he sets out to prove to himself that he is still number one, but when everything starts to go wrong for him, he learns what it really means to be #1.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Diminishing Discourse
description: Elliott and Frankie decide to tell Mo about what really happened to the dinosaurs.

title: Fistfull of Balloons
description: When Vic gets double-crossed during a water balloon fight, he goes on a revenge mission to find out who was responsible.

title: La Hora Mas Oscura
description: Los Ninjas, los Munces y los Geckles se refugian en la Cueva Fuerte Geckle , pero enfrentan al Hechicero Calavera y al Dragón Grief-Bringer.

title: Roundabout
description: Forever Knight finally assembles his Round Table of young but super-powerful Knights, including Ben? With his squires' help, Forever Knight turns a Particle Accelerator into a Time Machine and sets out to conquer all of history, but a certain hero with a team of 10 aliens on his side has other plans foiling Forever Knight at every twist and turn in time while Grandpa Max, Gwen and Phil keep the rest of the Round Table busy in the present.

title: Prankless
description: The guys want to win a prank war with a rival park.

title: Last One There
description: When Unikitty accidentally invokes an ancient curse, the gang must beat Master Frown and Brock back to the castle before one of them literally turns into a rotten egg.

title: The Birthday to End All Birthdays
description:
Unikitty and the gang secretly throw Master Frown the birthday of his dreams, but their efforts have lasting repercussions beyond Frown's special day./
Following the events of Master Frown's birthday, Unikitty and her friends form a resistance group to restore the Unikingdom.

title: Letter Wronging Campaign
description: When Prohyas sends Vambre for a much needed spa day, he drafts Noville to help on a mission to discover why all the books in the Library of Shhhhh are blank.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Masters Never Quit
description: Pursued by a magma monster, Cole, Princess Vania, Wu & the Lowly arrive at a mysterious temple deep in Shintaro Mountain, a temple which was once a training ground for Earth Elementals including Cole's own mother, Lilly!

title: Karate Mom
description: After surprising Clarence with Martial Arts classes at the "Aberdojo," Mary gets talked into joining the class herself. She loves the slow-paced lessons in discipline and control, but Clarence just wants to have fun and kick butt! Can Mary convince Clarence to stick with the class, earn his belt and have some fun with her?

title: Let's Fight to the End
description: When a fighting tournament is announced at the Plaza, there is more at stake than meets the eye.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: The Duke
description: Finn goes to great lengths to catch the evil Duke of Nuts, only to discover he's not such a bad guy after all.

title: The Zoo
description: Steven visits a special zoo.

title: Candy Is Dandy/Catastrophe
description: Candy Is Dandy: When the Mayor gives the girls some candy in gratitude for saving the day, they become hooked on the stuff. They even make a deal with a local villain to commit crimes for treats./Catastrophe: A monster is frantically tearing up the town looking for his lost kitty. But in a city the size of Townsville, how can the girls find one lone cat?

title: Burlate con Todas tus Fuerzas
description: Cuando Adorabat empieza a interrumpir agresivamente a todos con su nuevo poder que le da energía, se convierte en una amenaza para el reino entero.

title: Mas del canal de todos
description: A través de otra sesión de navegación por Internet, vemos más videos subidos por los Osos y sus amigos.

title: Fragments
description: Steven heads to the woods to train with a powerful mentor.

title: The Drip
description: Robin finally experiences drip, a magical coolness that comes from wearing sneakers, and soon seeks out the ultimate pair.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: A Made Up Story
description: Someone is defacing all the posters and statues of Townsville with make-up. Can the girls stop this makeover takeover or will they get the blush off?

title: The Unikingdom Awards
description: Unikitty throws an elaborate award show for everyone in the Unikingdom, including Master Frown and Brock, but tensions rise when Frown fails to win an award.

title: Patty's Law
description: If found guilty of breaking Patty's Law, Apple and Onion face grave punishment but they have a more pressing concern; looking after their dear, sickly Falafel.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: #TrianguloDeOdio
description: Cuando la exnovia de Hal aparece en el partido de bienvenida de la preparatoria Metrópolis y se enfurece por amor, convertida en la villana Star Sapphire, Jessica comienza a cuestionar sus propias tácticas no violentas.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Crece
description: Mientras todo el mundo celebra a Valentino porque le creció su primer vello facial, Vic se pone celoso y recurre a métodos mágicos para dejarse crecer el bigote y competir por la atención.

title: Face of the Town!
description: Mayor Huckleberry holds a city-wide contest to find out which Jellystone citizen most represents the town.

title: Caza o Juego
description: Después de recibir un billete superexclusivo para Adrenalandia, Ben deja atrás al abuelo Max y a Gwen para disfrutar de las ventajas de ser el único asistente del parque. Pero pronto se entera de que no está solo.

title: La Explosion de Fuego Colosal
description: Cuando Colosal sale de un extraño estado de creatividad producto de una concentración extrema, es posible que haya hecho algo que podría destruir el Valle Puro Corazón entero.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Super Caillou!/Trip on the Subway/Caillou's Race/As Good as New/I, Robot
description: Caillou just loves his Superbear storybook./Caillou learns to deal with a change in plans when Daddy has to use the car./Caillou is playing a board game with Mom and he gets a little upset./Caillou learns about 'recycling' -- literally!/ When Sarah shows Caillou and Leo her new remote controlled robot, the boys get a great idea to be robots too!

title: Sleepover at JP's
description: JP invites his friends over for a sleepover, but it happens to be on the night of a huge game of Flashlight Tag in the Creek!

title: Ralph
description: Charlie conoce a una criatura igual a él llamada Ralph. A Charlie le encanta tener un amigo nuevo, pero los Osos piensan que Ralph no trae nada bueno entre manos.

title: The Eater
description: It's Halloween and Apple's not feeling quite right. He takes Onion into the dark depths to find out why.

title: Out of My Head
description: Axel must help Sarge and Bobbie learn to walk in each other's shoes - literally - after Luka unwittingly switches the toys' heads!

title: Falafel's Passion
description: Apple and Onion try to help Falafel find his passion but it looks like things might take a humiliating turn.

title: El Centro Comercial
description: Los Osos van al centro comercial y se encuentran con sus equivalentes humanos.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: House Flies Don't Dance/Flying the Nest/The Insult
description: Lucas and Maizie help Findley learn to dance./ Arlo believes he's a big owl now, so it's time to fly his nest. But is Arlo ready to leave his friends behind?/ When Lucas calls Findley a mean name, he tries to make things right again.

title: Who's the Fake?!/Trouble Busters! 2
description: With the reveal that Haavik is a shapeshifting Alien, the ABs start to get super-paranoid, realizing that ANYONE could be Haavik in disguise. The suspicion quickly turns inward, and the ABs are left wondering if they have an imposter among them!/ A kid brawler named Oliver has lost his Bakugan! This seems like a job for the Trouble Busters. The Awesome Brawlers help him chase down and try to catch the elusive Bakugan, who leads them on a wild goose chase through Los Volmos.

title: That Slobot Is No Bot of Mine
description: Axel and the team compete against themselves in tests of skill, strength, and stamina, but when SloBot gets belittled, he splits into three separate robots - each with their own evil personalities!

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: The Prank
description: Gumball and Darwin's harmless pranks on Dad spiral hopelessly out of control.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Ahora Te Toca a Ti, Amigo
description: Axel y el equipo giran las bromas de camuflaje de Galileo sobre él, convenciendo al crédulo gecko de que es permanentemente invisible, ipara obtener resultados desastrosos!

title: Zing Your Heart Out
description: When Adorabat starts to aggressively heckle everyone with her new zing power, she threatens the entire kingdom.

title: Forever Road
description: During a drag race, Ben hopes to stay neck and neck with Vin Ethanol and La Grange as XLR8, but when his watch keeps shorting out, our hero must get creative if he is to keep up with his fast and furious foes!

title: Ninos del Perro
description: Craig ha intentado que su familia adopte un perro durante años, pero nunca lo logró. Puede que ahora tenga una oportunidad si sigue los consejos de un carismático niño del bosque y su programa de tres pasos.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Melancholic Megalomaniac
description: Elliott and Mo try to cheer up Lord Kallous, with the help of someone from his past.

title: Ralph
description: Charlie meets a creature just like him named Ralph. Charlie loves having a new friend, but the Bears think Ralph is bad news.

title: Snow Place Like Home
description: When the Bears realize whatever they build with snow comes to life they decide to build the biggest snow party of all time.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Churro Kings
description: When Vic & Val start making good money from selling churros at the taco stand, their lust for stuff makes them do dirty tricks to take out their competition.

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: The Game
description: The Wattersons embark on their first family game of Dodge or Dare, but soon find out why Gumball and Darwin abandoned the monster they created.

title: Continue?
description: The Mysterious Hooded Woman hires the Warriors to retrieve the Orb of Sphericity from a temple in Galacton. The odd thing is, this temple has save points! When the Warriors are defeated, they respawn, but Vambre remembers what happened and Prohyas does not.

title: Chess Master Steve
description: Pizza Steve goes to great lengths in order to beat Mr. Gus at a game of chess.

title: Dibble's Dust-Up
description: Grumpy's determination to get the Cloudseeker clean is comically thwarted when Dibble befriends a stowaway trio of cute dust bunnies.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Dendy's Video Channel
description: Dendy tries to update KO's Video Channel for him, but has trouble finding something to post.

title: Hula Hoop
description: Coco is showing Bing her new Holly Hula Hoop, but will be Bing be able to hula like Coco?

title: Ticking Crime Bomb
description: Leshawna and Izzy trick Owen into thinking he's destined to be a criminal mastermind, but when he leaves school to join the scariest gang in town, they have to mount a rescue attempt.

title: Cuenta Regresiva
description: Axel tiene que limpiar la sala de estar a tiempo para la cena de su tío, pero tratar de hacer demasiado de una vez lo deja atrapado como un juguete con Orangutank suelto y menos de una hora hasta que lleguen los invitados.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Los de Arriba Contra Atacan
description: Cole y los de abajo llegan para rescatar a los Ninjas. Para ello, Cole tendrá que recuperar las espadas legendarias, las Espadas de la Liberación.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Big Boots
description: Bing and Sula are being giants and splashing in puddles with their rainy boots. What will happen when Bing finds a big puddle?

title: Sale el Don
description: Cuando Vic y Val descubren que Don Jalapeño no es realmente él mismo, depende de ellos usar el alocado libro de conspiraciones de Don para salvarlo.

title: Giving
description: It's Sula's birthday! Bing is choosing the perfect present for her, but really loves it himself. Will Bing keep the present for himself?

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Oracle
description: Banana Barbara has made a prophecy which Gumball simply cannot accept. Gumball, Darwin and Anais discover that Banana Joe's mom paints pictures which predict the future. When they find one that depicts Gumball running naked through the mall, Gumball is determined not to let it come to pass. However events conspire against him, and Gumball learns that sometimes you can't fight fate.

title: Los reyes de los Churros
description: Cuando Vic y Val comienzan a hacer dinero con la venta de churros en el puesto de tacos, su deseo por objetos los obliga a emplear trucos sucios para eliminar a la competencia.

title: Joke's on You, Bro!
description: Axel and the team turn Galileo's camouflaging pranks around on him, convincing the gullible gecko that he's permanently invisible - to disastrous results!

title: Exquisite Grandpa
description: Uncle Grandpa has been having some truly bizarre night terrors.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: The Sandman Is Coming
description: Daffy thinks the Sandman is a monster that throws sand in children's eyes.

title: Hashtag #1 Fan
description: Panda gets kidnapped by a pair of deranged French foxes.

title: 150-Piece Kit
description: Benson wants to prove that he performed a famous drum solo.

title: School's In, Oh Bummer
description: It turns out that Vambre and Prohyas didn't graduate the Adventure Academy after all and need to go back to school earn their diplomas!

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Dancing at Grandma's/Mystery Valentine/Play Ball!/Dogsled Ahead!
description: It is a rainy day and Caillou is disappointed because he will not be able to go play at the park with Grandma./It's Valentine's day and Caillou is invited to a Valentine's party at his best friend Leo's house./When Dad's baseball team, the Tigers, are playing a game at the park, Caillou, Rosie and Mom go to cheer him on./Caillou and his family are heading to the tobogganing hill!

title: La noche que Ben Tennyson vino al pueblo
description: El equipo Tennyson viaja a Wheeler, "la ciudad minera más animada de la Ruta 66". Pero cuando Ben se pone paranoico con la idea de que el Caballero por Siempre lo esté persiguiendo, debe tratar de convencer a su familia al mismo tiempo que evita que su nuevo enemigo destruya la ciudad.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: No Honor Among Bros
description: Rook is under the influence of Fistrick's "bro" essence, and starts to act like a bro. Can he and Ben infiltrate an alien fight club to claim the Golden Fist? (Introducing Slix Vigma, alien promoter.)

title: #ConoceAGuepardo
description: Barbara Minerva está super celosa de la "pequeña señorita perfecta" Diana Prince. Pero cuando usa un antiguo artefacto de la colección de su padre para lanzar una maldición contra Diana, la maldición se vuelve en su contra.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Tea Timer's Ball
description: The Tea Timers throw a dance and invite everyone in the Creek. Craig believes it's solely to prank him, while Kelsey deals with an unwanted admirer.

title: Safari Joe
description: While minding her own business, Cheetara is caught in a trap set by Safari Joe, the famously annoying hunter! After escaping, she rallies the other ThunderCats to help her stop Joe once and for all, by turning the tables and capturing him!

title: Fuera de hora
description: Cuando las advertencias de Harold de no meterse con el reloj son ignoradas, los niños están obligados a salvarse a sí mismos cuando Duncan abre un agujero en la trama del tiempo.

title: Bolos para Campeonas
description: Axel y el equipo deben intervenir cuando la competencia de bolos no tan amigable de Zoe con Cleo LeBall es interrumpida por Madcap, Porcupunk y su nueva cohorte, el travieso Dynamo magnético.

title: Cousin Jon
description: When the Bears attend Chloe's family reunion, they fall victim to the mischievous pranks of Chloe's cousin, Jon.

title: Fun Dungeon Face Off
description: Clarence's Mom treats Clarence, Jeff and Sumo to an afternoon at Rough Riders Chicken, a fast food restaurant with a play emporium. When Clarence and Sumo steal Jeff's fries, Jeff is forced to confront his germ phobias head-on in the restaurant's seemingly unsanitary play area.

title: Field Trip
description: A group of teenage superheroes are being shown around the Fortress of Solitude when they inadvertently cause the phantom zone projector to trap Superman and release three Kryptonian criminals.

title: Congelados
description: Axel y su equipo se encuentran en una posición difícil después de que Ice Crusher hace demasiado frío para que puedan defenderse a toda velocidad.

title: The Dream Team
description: Craig and his cousin, Bryson, join forces for an action packed weekend at their grandparents house.

title: See You There
description: Mordecai and Rigby find out that everyone has been invited by Muscle Man to High Five Ghost's birthday party except them. They decide to go anyway.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Prey or Play
description: After receiving a super-exclusive ticket to Adrenaland, Ben leaves behind Grandpa Max and Gwen to enjoy the perks of being the parks only attendant, but when he learns he's not alone, our hero must now contend with the only kid who could afford the price of admission: Billy Billions!

title: #MeetTheCheetah
description: Barbara Minerva is super-jealous of  "little Miss Perfect" Diana Prince. But when she uses an ancient artifact from her dad's collection to place a curse on Diana, it turns out that Diana's not the one who's cursed. It's Barbara.

title: Venganza apestosa
description: Cuando una mofeta viene a buscar su venganza anual contra el Chef, Duncan ve una oportunidad de tomarse unas vacaciones de la guardería.

title: Homeworld Bound
description: Steven heads to the Diamonds for advice on how to control his new powers.

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Carl
description: A pleasant weekend goes awry when a monster attacks.

title: El primo Jon
description: Cuando los Osos asisten a una reunión con la familia de Chloe, se convierten en víctimas de Jon, el travieso primo de Chloe.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: #AdventuresInBunnysitting
description: Zee asks Kara to look after her two magical bunnies, which quickly start to multiply, wreaking havoc all across Metropolis.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Monster Reunion
description: Steven reunites with an old friend.

title: The Ascent
description: Cole, the Lowly, Princess Vania and Wu discover that the stone-mech is fueled by Elemental Power, and attach it to the mine-carts in an effort to blast their way out of the mountain to confront the evil Skull Sorcerer!

title: The Lonely Haunts Club 3: La Llorona
description: When Val sets out to get a little privacy in the woods, Vic is bent on pranking his unsuspecting brother,  that is, until Val goes missing.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: Batman vs. Teen Titans: Dark Injustice
description: The Titans try to outprank each other on April Fools' Day.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Caillou's Favorite Plate/Fun in the Mud/All Aboard!/I Scream for Ice Cream/Gilbert's House
description: Grandma has given Caillou a special spaceship plate./It's raining outside but there is no stopping Caillou!/After finding a photograph of a four-year-old Dad with a model train set, Caillou and Dad decide to look for it./When Caillou spots a dog house outside he gets the idea that Gilbert might like a house of his own./Caillou, Rosie and Mom are having fun at the park when the ice-cream man comes around.

title: Fire & Ice
description: Kelsey and Stacks write a story for book club, which turns out to be more personal than Kelsey realized.

title: Perfect Day
description: Ben thinks he's having 'the perfect day' only to realize he's been put in a dream world by Enoch and the Forever Knights who are after the Omnitrix. Ben's "dream world" soon becomes a nightmare world, with Ben forced to live out his ultimate terror...being stuck at school! But with Max and Gwen's help, he's able to vanquish his nightmare foes and re-enter the real world where he takes down  Enoch...only to reveal an even more powerful knight...The Forever King.

title: La Aventura Perfecta
description: Cuando a Mao Mao se le antoja vivir la aventura perfecta, Adorabat dice una mentira piadosa.

title: El Benefactor
description: Los Osos ayudan a Chloe a presentar su proyecto de ciencias para un concurso escolar. Pero el rival de Chloe complica las cosas.

title: The Upply Strike Back!
description: Cole and the Upply arrive at the Skull Sorcerer's keep in the hopes of rescuing Lloyd and the other ninja. But in order to do so, Cole will need to retrieve his mother's fabled swords, the Blades of Deliverance, which are hidden somewhere inside the keep!

title: Lost in the Supermarket
description: During a trip to the supermarket with his mom, Clarence discovers produce adventure and coupon intrigue in aisle five...and every other aisle.

title: The Escape Room of Doom
description: The gang infiltrate an escape room game center to thwart Score Creeper, but their former foe claims he only works there to pay the bills.

title: A Dog's Life
description: Pocoyo pretends to be an elephant, a duck and a dog - but when Loula needs his help, Pocoyo sees that sometimes it's best just to be himself.

title: Pijamada en casa de JP
description: JP invita a sus amigos para una pijamada, pero resulta ser la misma noche que un gran juego con linternas en el Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: And Then There Were None
description: Vilgax and Eon team up to wipe out every Ben in every dimension!

title: #LaCubetaDeBurritos
description: A Babs le encanta su trabajo en el restaurante de comida rápida "La Cubeta de Burritos" , pero a su jefe, que está harto de que ella siempre llegue tarde y de su enorme dispersión, le encantaría encontrar cualquier excusa para despedirla. Cuando se produce un robo a un banco que está enfrente de su trabajo, Babs no puede decidir si encarnar su papel de superheroína o el de empleada obediente de La Cubeta. Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Thomas' Day Off
description: When all the trains but Thomas get deliveries, he's left to spend the day alone. With the help of an old boxcar and a battered beachball... an adventure unfolds.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Jewel of the Aisle/Super Zeroes
description: Jewel of the Isle: A crook hides a huge diamond in a box of the girls' favorite cereal. But how can he trick the girls into giving him some cereal in order to get the jewel back?/Super Zeroes: The girls don't think they have enough superhero accessories like those found in the comic books. They begin to emulate their favorite characters, complete with gadgets and gizmos.

title: Watch It!
description: The Powerpuff Girls are tasked with keeping a priceless gem safe from thieves.

title: The Mall
description: The Bears go the mall and encounter their human counterparts.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Uncle Grandpa: The High School Years
description: Uncle Grandpa and friends go way back to when they were in high school together.

title: Pie Contest
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to prove to Benson that they can be judges at the pie contest.

title: Picture This
description: Pocoyo imagines that fish live in different places and draws funny pictures for his friends.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: Caillou's Sleepover Guest/Games in the Park/The Sugar Shack/Winter Mystery/Caillou's Snowday
description: Leo is spending the night at Caillou's./Caillou is excited when Miss Martin takes him and his friends to the park for some special activities./When Caillou's family makes a springtime visit to Jonas' ranch, he takes them on a sleigh ride./The twins, Jason and Jeffrey, have come to play with Caillou in the snow./When Caillou, Rosie and Mom head to the big park, Caillou sees André.

title: Ghosted
description: Vic makes a ghost friend but when she interferes with his shot at being part of the cool kids' Tlatchtli team, he must choose between the two.

title: Quest for Knowledge
description: After a flashback where we learn the origins of the Warriors passion for Magiswords, they return to Adventure Academy where Professor Cyrus sets V and P and their former classmates on a quest to find the Legendary Knowledge Magisword.

title: Van Hogling
description: Chef and the kids take a field trip to Sugar's farm but  ignore all of Sugar's strict and boring farm rules has dire consequences when Chef and the kids unleash a herd of ravenous "Were-hogs" on a full moon.

title: The Son of Lilly
description: The battle for the fate of Shintaro Mountain concludes!

title: Summer Fun Day!
description: The Thundercats are exhausted from fighting bad guys all the time so Lion-O suggests they spend a relaxing summer fun day at the beach, with no fighting! Unfortunately the beach is home to the Crabmen, giant, clawed humanoids that fight anyone who steps on their sand! Looks like summer fun day might involve some fighting!

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Man Up 4: The Donnyest Game
description: With Man-Boy on the loose, Donny must be prepared for anything.

title: More Everyone's Tube
description: Through another video browsing session online, we get more videos uploaded by the Bears and their friends.

title: That Will Be All
description: Steven and the Gems make a daring escape!

title: Weapon XI Part 1
description: Kevin and Argit attempt to warn the amalgam kids about the Rooters intentions meanwhile Ben, Rook, and Gwen set off to find Kevin and land themselves in the Null Void!

title: Restaurant Wars
description: Steven must help the Frymans and the Pizzas settle a reignited rivalry between their restaurants.

title: Carretera por Siempre
description: Durante una carrera de aceleración, Ben espera mantenerse al mismo nivel con Vin Etanol y La Grange como XLR8. Pero cuando su reloj hace cortocircuito una y otra vez, nuestro héroe debe ser creativo si quiere seguir el ritmo de sus rápidos y furiosos enemigos.

title: Mushpot's Treasure
description: When Mushpot wishes he could roll back the seasons and relive being a Mushler, our friends get him to hang out doing cool Mushler stuff. But this just shows that Mushpot is no longer able to do all those things. Sigh! However, when our friends find a map that points to a treasure he buried when he was a Mushler, Mushpot realises it's just the Mushler experience he needed.

title: The Uploads
description: Gumball and Darwin try to tear themselves away from the internet, but end up falling down the Elmore Stream-hole.

title: Ghostboy
description: Starfire mistakenly thinks she's killed Beast Boy, leading him to pose as a ghost and torment her.

title: The Past Revealed/Run! A Storm's on the Way
description: The Past Revealed: After getting lost in maze with Lia, Ajit remembers the day he met Pharol and Auxilataur. He finally can explain how he was able to partner with golden Bakugan, but Ajit's story is interrupted by a familiar face - Storm!/Run! A Storm's on the Way: Still upset that Ajit has given up his life as a phantom thief, Storm rolls out Hydranoid x Aquos and attacks! Ajit and Lia take off running through the maze as Storm gives chase.

title: Lion-S
description: Lion-O and the other ThunderCats are thrilled to meet a brand new Thunderian: Lion-S! She's cool, good at fighting robots and, most importantly, thinks Lion-O and his Sword of Omens are really neat and interesting! Looks like the ThunderCats have a new best friend! Maybe even, a new ThunderCat?????

title: Adorapapa
description: Cuando el papa de Adorabat le prohíbe trabajar en el departamento del sheriff porque es muy peligroso, Adorabat decide demostrarle que puede cuidarse sola.

title: #HateTriangle
description: When Hal's ex-girlfriend shows up at the Metropolis High homecoming game and goes love-ballistic as the villain Star Sapphire, Jessica begins to second-guess her own nonviolent tactics.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Harold Swatter and the Goblet of Flies
description: After finding what he believes to be a magic wand, Owen accidentally turns Harold into a housefly.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Red Action 3: Grudgement Day
description: KO and Enid attempt to prevent a mysterious power battle between Rad and Red Action.

title: Sideline Dad
description: When the Girls start playing soccer, the Professor goes overboard.

title: Badge-a-fire Explosion
description: When BC comes out of a rare state of hyper-focused creativity, he may have made something that could destroy all of PHV.

title: The Children of the Dog
description: Craig has tried to convince his family to get a dog for years but has never been successful, but he may have a chance if he follows the guidance of a charismatic creek kid and her three step program.

title: Get That BORFL!
description: A restful chill day for the Warriors and Princess Zange in the Royal Spa gets upended when a cute little Borfl runs amok throughout Castle Rhyboflaven, with the Warriors resorting to Magiswords to thwart the critter.

title: The Perfect Adventure
description: When Mao Mao gets hungry for the perfect adventure, Adorabat tells a white lie.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Dusk Industries Under Attack/Taking Dan Back
description: Dusk Industries Under Attack: "Bad Dan" has his taken his rampage to Dusk Industries and this time he has help spreading the chaos and destruction, he's joined by Sophie, McQ, Everett, Storm and Haavik! The Awesome Brawlers are quickly on the scene try to bring an end to the show of destruction./ Taking Dan Back: "Bad Dan" with Haavik's crew and their fusion Bakugan continue the rampage at Dusk Industries. The Awesome Brawlers, with some help from Magnus, are determined to an end to this show of destruction and get their friend back!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: The Night Ben Tennyson Came to Town
description: Team Tennyson travels to Wheeler, "the liveliest mining town on Route 66", but when Ben becomes paranoid that the Forever Knight is out to get him, he must try to convince his fam while also stopping his new foe from destroying the town.

title: El baile de los Infusionistas
description: Los Infusionistas organizan un baile e invitan a todos los habitantes del bosque. Craig cree que el único propósito del baile es hacerle una broma a él, mientras que Kelsey debe lidiar con un admirador indeseado.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Freezer Burn
description: Batman and Firestorm team up to fight their respective cold villains, Mr. Freeze and Killer Frost. Complications arise when Firestorm's infatuation for the wily Ms. Frost gets the best of him.

title: Wallpaper Man
description: Mordecai and Rigby are driving to a Halloween party and tell scary stories to pass the time.

title: Fussy Duck
description: Pato, fresh from his shower, is determined to keep clean. Pocoyo and Elly have very different ideas, and Pato soon realizes that half the fun of getting clean is getting dirty in the first place!

title: Don't Drink the Water
description: In Florida, Ben and Max accidentally come in contact with water from The Fountain of Youth. As a result, Max transforms into a kid and Ben a toddler, with Gwen having to deal with both of them. Our trio then must track down Hex who's found the source of the fountain and prevent him from drinking the water that will make him immortal and unstoppable.

title: Bubbles
description: Bing and Pando are learning how to make bubbles, but will Bing be able to blow his own bubble?

title: Tiny Miracle's Tiny Miracle
description: Upon seeing the gang have a fun time swimming and eating ice cream, Tiny Miracle realizes he wants to be a real boy.

title: The Rooters of All Evil
description: Meet the Rooters, the Black Ops wing of the Plumbers from the Null Void. They've come looking for someone close to Ben, and they mean business!

title: Luthor in Paradise
description: With the aid of Circe the Witch, Luthor travels to Paradise Island to steal an artifact that will give him god-like powers. When Superman and Batman arrive on the island to bring him back, they find that they're almost as popular with the Amazons as Luthor on this woman-only island.

title: Caillou's Gym Day/Our Rocket Ship/Caillou Helps Grandpa/The Backyard Bowlers/Caillou's Milk Run
description: Caillou gets a special invitation to go to André's gym class./Caillou and Leo are playing with their rocket ships in the park./On a winter day, Dad and Caillou go over to Grandpa's with their skates./When Caillou and Rosie stay at Grandma and Grandpa's house, Grandpa uses pop bottles and a rubber ball to create a kid's bowling alley./Caillou accidentally spills the rest of the milk before Rosie could get her cereal.

title: Rumbo al Planeta Madre
description: Steven acude a las Diamantes para pedirles consejos sobre cómo controlar sus nuevos poderes.

title: The Darkest Hour
description: Forced to flee by the arrival of Grief-Bringer, the ninja, the Munce and the Geckles take refuge in the Geckle Strong-Cave. But the bitter feud between Munce and Geckles threatens to tear them apart, just when unity is needed most…when they are about to confront the Skull Sorcerer and Grief-Bringer!

title: The Best Robin
description: When the other Titans are too lazy to fight Brother Blood, Robin calls on his secondary team: Team Robin, a crime-fighting group made up of different Robins.

title: Stink. Stank. Stunk
description: When a skunk comes seeking its annual revenge on Chef, Duncan sees it as an opportunity to get a vacation from daycare.

title: Golden Bakugan Encounter/Ties of Gold
description: Golden Bakugan Encounter: Dan and Shun, split up from the rest of Awesome Brawlers, are traveling in through the maze when they discover McQ. It turns out McQ is seeking a golden Bakugan. When the boys go in for a closer look, they are startled by an old friend, and together confront McQ./Ties of Gold: The now reunited Awesome Brawlers are once again confronted by Storm, McQ, Sophie and Everett, who are on the hunt for golden Bakugan. With tired Bakugan, the Awesome Brawlers will have to give it their all to defend against this evil.

title: El Hijo de Lilly
description: iLa batalla por el destino de la Montaña Shintaro concluye!

title: The Vengers
description: Billy Billions, Kangaroo Kommando, and Captain Nemesis team up to take down Ben, and claim his place as protector of Bellwood?!?

title: Rage of the Red Lanterns
description: Chased by the Red Lanterns, Lobo seeks sanctuary with the Justice League. As the League attempts to stave off the Red Lanterns, Lobo reveals the real reason he wants shelter in the Watchtower, he wants access to a powerful space weapon being held by our heroes.

title: Donny
description: In an attempt to save a village, Finn and Jake rehabilitate Donny the Ogre, who's a real jerk.

title: #Beeline
description: Cuando tropieza con un malvado complot para hacer explotar un puente de la ciudad, Bumblebee se espanta y acude a sus amigas para que derroten a los malhechores. Pero cuando todas sus super amigas están ocupadas, Bumblebee debe buscar cada gramo de coraje en ella para hacer frente a la situación, a pesar de ser la más pequeña del grupo.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: El Ascenso
description: Cole, los de abajo, la princesa Vania y Wu salen de la montaña para enfrentarse al malvado Hechicero Calavera.

title: Storytime
description: It's bath time and Bing's reading his favourite story. When the book falls in the bath, how will Bing read the story?

title: #Beeline
description: When she stumbles across a villainous plot to blow up a bridge, Bumblebee shies from the challenge of taking on the baddies and reaches out to her friends. But when the other heroes are all indisposed, it'll take every ounce of courage Bumblebee has to rise to the occasion … despite being the smallest of the bunch.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Operation Tin Man
description: Gizmo convinces the Titans he's kidnapped Cyborg, when in reality Cyborg's just hanging out in the HIVE tower with his girl Jinx. When Gizmo gets annoyed by Cyborg's constant presence, the two start a prank war.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Hole In Roof
description: Suddenly the hole in the roof is no longer a laughing matter but one of a life or death.

title: The Oct-Father
description: When Princess Morbucks steals Octi, Bubbles' reaction surprises everyone, even her sisters.

title: One Wise Bear
description: The Bears become lost in the Valley of Whispering Winds, where voices whisper in their ears and make them lose faith in themselves. Racing to their rescue, Tenderheart leads them to the only one who knows the antidote to the words of the Winds: a mysterious old bear of great wisdom who teaches them a valuable lesson about listening to your heart.

title: Nightmare/Bad Dan
description: Nightmare: Dan hasn't been sleeping well lately. No "sleep brawling" this time, but he's constantly tossing and turning. It turns out, Dan's dreams have been hijacked by Haavik, who's trying to spread his vision of chaos and destruction to Dan!/Bad Dan: Haavik has taken control of Dan and sends him on a Bakugan rampage! With "Bad Dan" causing all kinds of havoc and destruction, the rest of the Awesome Brawlers have no choice but to roll out to try to contain "Bad Dan".

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Adoradad
description: When AD's dad forbids her from working with the Sheriff's Dept because it's too dangerous, AD sets out to prove that she can take care of herself.

title: Fuera de Mi Cabeza
description: iAxel debe ayudar a Sarge y Bobbie a aprender a caminar en los zapatos del otro, literalmente, después de que Luka involuntariamente cambia las cabezas de los juguetes!

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: When Wedding Bells Thaw
description: Finn must help plan the Ice King's bachelor party.

title: I'll Do it in a Minute/Cloud Gazing/Don't Do That Arlo
description: Arlo has fun playing, but he procrastinates when it comes to tidying up./ Lucas, Arlo, and Findley have a day of make-believe with the clouds./ Arlo can't resist the temptation to look into next door's garden through a knothole.

title: Fear in the Family
description: Ben and Gwen can't wait for the Omni-Copter to arrive at the Great Pyramids, but when bad weather disrupts their flight, they soon come face-to-face with The Fogg and its spawn: The Fogg Family!

title: Duelo de globos
description: Cuando Vic es traicionado durante una guerra de globos de agua, emprende una vengativa misión para descubrir al responsable.

title: Countdown
description: Axel has to clean up the living room in time for his uncle's dinner party, but trying to do too much at once leaves him stuck as a toy with Orangutank on the loose and less than an hour until the guests arrive.

title: Fragmentos
description: Steven se dirige al bosque para entrenarse con un poderoso mentor.

title: The Tag
description: Gumball and Darwin get caught in the middle of Dad and Mr Robinson's trashcan feud.

title: Clarence's Millions
description: When Clarence realizes the classroom "buddy star" system is leaving some kids behind, he creates his own form of currency called "Clarence Dollars." The new reward system promptly turns the entire school upside down.

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 2
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Thank You for Watching the Show
description: When KO finds moments of his life slipping by, he begins to suspect something weird is going on.

title: Henchman
description: While trying to rescue a helpless stranger, Finn becomes Marceline's slave.

title: Pocoyolympics
description: Pocoyo, Elly and Pato stage their own version of the olympics - with a funny and very original variety of contests.

title: Prince Starling's Quest
description: Lion-O is happily playing with Snarf in their "Frolicking Field" and doesn't have a care in the world, unfortunately he's accidentally stomping all over the miniature village of the Micrits! The tiny people want to defeat the "giant orange monster" but such a quest would require a brave hero. Luckily, the Micrits have such a hero: Prince Starling! Now, let us the tell you the epic tale of Prince Starling as he journeys to find the fountain of growth and defeat the wicked Lion-O, who has no idea any of this is going on!

title: Uncle Greedpa
description: Uncle Grandpa is in need of some extra cash, so he starts charging for his services.

title: #BurritoBucket
description: Babs loves her job at fast food restaurant Burrito Bucket, but her boss, who's fed up with her chronic lateness and bad case of scatterbrain, would love any excuse to fire her. When a bank robbery breaks out right across the street from work, Babs is torn between her role as a superhero and dutiful Burrito Bucket employee. Will she be able to save the day and keep her job all in the nick of time?

title: Whale's Birthday
description: It's Whale's birthday. When all of Whale's presents get spoiled on the way to the party, Pocoyo, Elly and Pato are sad. But Whale is happy just to see them. Friends are what you need for a party!

title: Drama Bomb
description: The school play goes off the rails when the drama teacher interferes.

title: The Headsucker's Moxy/Equal Fights
description: The Headsucker's Moxy: There's a mysterious villain in town who's sucking pertinent information from the brains of powerful people and committing crimes. How do the girls trap this sucker before his next victim is drained?/Equal Fights: When the girls try to catch a local female villain, she tells them that as women they've got to stick together. It's up to the women of Townsville to teach our heroines the true meaning of equality.

title: Jeff's New Toy
description: Jeff wants to keep his new, flying "Wrath Hover Ginsbot" toy in its box. Clarence is desperate to play with the toy. And poor Sumo is caught in the middle.

title: Look Who's Clocking
description: When Harold's warnings not to mess with the clock go ignored, the kids are forced to save themselves when Duncan tears a hole in the fabric of time.

title: Miedo en la Familia
description: Ben y Gwen están ansiosos por que el Omni-Copter llegue a las Grandes Pirámides. Pero cuando el mal tiempo interrumpe su vuelo, pronto se enfrentan cara a cara con Neblina y sus engendros: iLa familia Niebla!

title: Sabelotodo
description: Cuando Vic accidentalmente libera malvados murciélagos de una cueva, depende de los chicos y de Don proteger el pueblo, pero la actitud de sabelotodo de Vic pone en peligro la tarea.

title: Shine, Lilit, Shine
description: The Beacon Mushroom that guides the Mushables back to Mushton in the dark has gone out. So Lilit lights up and stands in its place for the night and soon gets quite bored! Lilit's good deed has her regretting her gift she's basically just a lamp! But when her light goes out, Lilit instantly regrets regretting it: she wants her gift back!

title: I Love You Mao Mao
description: An explosive loner and his slacker best friend are waylaid from their journey into legend, only to find that their story is just beginning.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Money Man
description: The Bears help Chloe present her project for a college science contest. But Chloe's rival makes things difficult.

title: Harold Matamoscas y el caliz de moscas
description: Después de descubrir lo que cree que es una varita mágica, Owen convierte accidentalmente a Harold en una mosca común.

title: Ratar-O
description: The ThunderCats have gotten so good at defeating the Mutants of Plun-Darr that it's basically become routine. That all changes with the arrival of the Mutants' old leader: Ratar-O, wielder of the Sword of Plun-Darr! Uh-oh!

title: DNA, A-OK!
description: Yogi finds out he's genetically a cat and joins Top Cat's gang.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Plastic Man Saves the World
description: Plastic Man feels shuffled off to the side as the Justice League battles Brainiac so he takes it upon himself to infiltrate the alien's ship on his own and thwart the villain's plans.

title: Rainy Day Daydream
description: Jake's imagination runs wild and Finn has to stop it before it kills them.

title: The Very Best Candy
description: The gang can't decide which of their candy is the best, so they turn it sentient and have it fight to determine the winner.
